<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span style="color:#006d98">وَأَمَّا الْإِجْمَاعُ:</span> فَقَدْ أَجْمَعَتِ الْأُمَّةُ عَلَى وُجُوبِ الحَجِّ عَلَى الْمُسْتَطِيعِ فِي الْعُمْرِ مَرَّةً وَاحِدَةً، وَكُفْرِ جَاحِدِهِ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>* * *<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span style="color:#006d98">س ١٥١:</span> مَا شُرُوطُ وُجُوبِ الْحَجِّ؟<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>شُرُوطُ الْحَجِّ خَمْسَةٌ،<span style="color:#006d98"> وَهِيَ:</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>١ - الْإِسْلَامُ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>٢ - الْعَقْلُ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>٣ - الْبُلُوغُ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>٤ - كَمَالُ الْحُرِّيَّةِ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>٥ - الاسْتِطَاعَةُ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>* * *<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span style="color:#006d98">س ١٥٢:</span> مَا أَنْوَاعُ أَنْسَاكِ الْحَجِّ؟<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>أَنْسَاكُ الْحَجِّ ثَلَاثَةُ أَنْوَاعٍ،<span style="color:#006d98"> وَهِيَ:</span><a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>١ -<span style="color:#006d98"> التَّمتُّع:</span> وَهُوَ الْإِحْرَامُ بِالْعُمْرَةِ فِي أَشْهُرِ الْحَجِّ، ثُمَّ التَّحَلُّلُ مِنْهَا، ثُمَّ الْإِحْرَامُ بِالْحَجِّ فِي يَوْمِ التَّرْوِيَةِ <span style="color:#008000">(وَهُوَ الْيَوْمُ الثَّامِنُ مِنْ ذِي الْحِجَّةِ)</span>.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>٢ -<span style="color:#006d98"> الْقِرَانُ:</span> وَهُوَ الْإِحْرَامُ بِالْعُمْرَةِ وَالْحَجِّ مَعًا.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>٣ -<span style="color:#006d98"> الْإِفْرَادُ:</span> وَهُوَ الْإِحْرَامُ بِالحَجِّ فَقَطْ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>